{"tid":2159097,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[皇仁舊生/學生入] 大家唔好忘記清算何君堯","createTime":"2020-08-16T06:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T10:44:10.000Z","uid":70915,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fedca254035868a6dae34ed01cf4aa26cc5dd73a","tid":2159097,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:12:11.000Z","msg":"代朋友po<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">TLDR：舊年12月，大比數舊生表態支持廢除何已完舊生會會籍，舊生會承諾跟進<br />\n<br />\n但過左大半年，連林鄭都俾人制裁喇，點解舊生會仲未做野？係咪想放生何妖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">皇仁舊生恥與何妖為伍</span></span><br />\n<br />\n全世界清算緊班狗官，721都過左一年，黑手何君堯有無受到影響？無！繼續上電視砌詞狡辯！<span class=\"gold\">所以就算幾小嘅一步，我地都要盡做！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">求幫推，求share俾皇仁舊生、學生、老師，向舊生會施壓</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n事件時序：<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8UXsZk0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8UXsZk0.png&h=0c7320a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d628400695dc91ea98bc613ccfc550908131c23","tid":2159097,"uid":70915,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:14:32.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\">我地曾經通過唔同渠道投稿，但廢何妖一事都得唔到太大關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝大家幫推</span><br />\n<br />\n皇仁舊生會執委會，你們何時才願意宣佈你們跟進終止何君堯的舊生會會籍的進度或結果？<br />\n <br />\n去年721事件發生後，當屆執委會迅速在翌日發出通告，表示會跟進終止會籍事宜，再在8月29日發出電郵徵詢會員相關意見。新一屆執委會，除了在去年12月14日的周年會員大會上回應過相關問題外，在這件事情上一直保持沉默，已經又過了半年，難道半年間跟進工作毫無進展？<br />\n <br />\n為甚麼你們保持沉默？<br />\n <br />\n是因為疫情而未能有效運作嗎？看來不是，2020年1月1日至7月19日期間，你們發出了四十多個通告，涵蓋年宵攤檔、舊生專訪、舊生演講、派發搓手液及口罩、舊生會餐廳及會所、悼念校友離世等，沒有一個月停止運作過。<br />\n <br />\n是因為疫情而未能開會嗎？看來這不是重要原因。雖然今年3月的會議的確開不成，可是2019年9月、2019年11月、2020年1月及2020年5月，執委會均有開會，出席率更是九成以上。更何況，上文提過去年7月22日發出通告和8月29日發出徵詢電郵，都是兩個會議之間發生的事情，證明除了議決終止會籍一事外，跟進行動不一定要等待執委會會議後才可以執行。<br />\n <br />\n是因為當事人不合作嗎？看來也不是。何某多次上過香港電台節目（包括《視點31》及《鏗鏘集》）公開回應721事件，推斷他不會拒絕皇仁舊生會的回應邀請吧？更何況去年9月他曾經在fb發文詢問過，是否應該先要給予他一個機會去回應。他主動提出的話，他自己不會反口吧？<br />\n <br />\n香港電台受盡打壓，依然敢就721事件追查到底，並訪問何君堯，可是皇仁舊生會執委會呢？是不發一言的縮頭烏龜？在施行拖字訣？還是已經有表決結果，卻不敢向會員公布？希望皇仁舊生會執委會，實際上不是想像中的那麼敗壞。<br />\n <br />\n皇仁舊生會執委會欠缺透明度，欠缺對會員的一個交待。請你們盡快回應，以釋疑慮。"},{"pid":"f8e7d685d670233b95e1d15768cc2ab2bad04670","tid":2159097,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:15:13.000Z","msg":"清算何妖，刻不容緩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a02ea9e4097cf41c8db53a8273504b930c563f","tid":2159097,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:15:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5d60473ea83d4836d4c64108a61743c02b31cd1","tid":2159097,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:16:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76d413e23dd9eda843490ea1552a8864c8b173b5","tid":2159097,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:17:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"60676fe88e33545cd13860b69accedc0495ed657","tid":2159097,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:19:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"386f6add5489430db9763e3531d4aa245c0a3564","tid":2159097,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:19:57.000Z","msg":"求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73639252a0fbff110349d668540c7f7cb23bae8","tid":2159097,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:21:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5968f89c5456a4fe4e426de831e35f2907e6c208","tid":2159097,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:23:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa952d68a9e86f04a75e500641b9fbdccbb876d0","tid":2159097,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"Agger <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee8fd2d66fce62b749db8abf28205fd697cb52a0","tid":2159097,"uid":313270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ab612e81a7d62b0b6202ca505be14fafe50cea","tid":2159097,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:19:58.000Z","msg":"推多幾下"},{"pid":"2ea134cee4173b98cfa9731c412ef32fbeaf228e","tid":2159097,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b84623d40394fcbea053649dae72acd6677aa6","tid":2159097,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:56:13.000Z","msg":"推到有舊生入黎留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f711ecfd721011a4856eeaec90935a7184f3d5","tid":2159097,"uid":77916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T01:56:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c9f072eece5ee81c8502ec78595dcfee68dc2bf","tid":2159097,"uid":372185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T01:59:34.000Z","msg":"一定要推上去"},{"pid":"6ae9db82fc43059fdf09e402380452d5e86850cb","tid":2159097,"uid":77916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T10:44:10.000Z","msg":"推"}]}